Learn how to control anxiety whenever you experience it. Try this breathing exercise to help alleviate your anxiety.  If your anxiety continues talk with your GP and ask if a referral to a psychiatrist is right for you. For more information visit https://t.co/pTAKDMK41P https://t.co/09y5ZrGetm

#Exercise improves mental health by reducing #anxiety, #depression, and negative mood and by improving self-esteem and cognitive function. Exercise has also been found to alleviate  symptoms such as low self-esteem and social withdrawal.

Exercise plays a much bigger role in a healthy lifestyle to reduce stress/anxiety. Eating healthy/sugar reduction,combined with exercise is a great combination. @USNewsHealth #gotoafitnesscenter #exerciseismedicine #gotoagym #learntoexercisecorrectly #healthylifestyle https://t.co/Y4jzedNibm
